(*About Me*) I am currently a research scientist at [https://miromind.ai/ MiroMind], Singapore, where I focus on AGI and its applications. My prior roles include an AI scientist at the Institute for Infocomm Research ([https://www.a-star.edu.sg/i2r I2R, A*STAR]) and a research fellow at the [https://www.nus.edu.sg NUS]. I earned my Ph.D. from the [https://www.usc.edu/ USC], Los Angeles, under the supervision of [https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/C.-C._Jay_Kuo C.C. Jay Kuo]. I have a strong record of academic contributions, with over 40 papers published in top-tier conferences and journals like ACL, EMNLP, NAACL, ACM KDD, TNNLS, and TASLP. My work has been recognized with multiple best paper awards. I have also served as the Publication Chair for EMNLP 2023 and as an editor for APSIPA Transactions.

(*Openings@MiroMind*) We have opening on *Interns* (paid) and *Full-Time* positions at MiroMind. Positions available in *Singapore, Beijing, and Shanghai*. Interested candidates are welcome to reach out via my email.

